# BUG REPORT (version-controlled)
# All fields required unless marked [optional]

BUG_ID: BUG-001
TITLE: Short problem description

SEVERITY: Blocker | Critical | High | Medium | Low

MODULE: recognition | product_card | prices | geolocation | history | auth | feedback | error_handling | ui

ENVIRONMENT:
  OS: Windows 11 / macOS 14 / Ubuntu 22
  BROWSER: Chrome 120 / Firefox 121 / Safari 17
  GEOLOCATION: enabled | disabled | denied

PRECONDITIONS:
  - e.g., "User is not authenticated"
  - "Geolocation is allowed"

STEPS_TO_REPRODUCE:
  1. Step 1
  2. Step 2
  3. Step 3

ACTUAL_RESULT:
  What actually happens

EXPECTED_RESULT:
  Expected behavior per spec

ATTACHMENTS: [optional] links to screenshots/videos (can be stored in .bugs/assets/)

ADDITIONAL_INFO: [optional] logs, API status, console errors

# Fields filled later (by engineer or automation)
STATUS: new | in_progress | fixed | rejected | duplicate
FIX_BRANCH: [optional]
DATE_CLOSED: [optional]
